#: src/Service/SiteAuditService.php:565
msgid "Anti-greenwashing module is disabled. It is good practice to store sources for environmental claims."
msgstr "Modul anti-greenwashing je deaktivovaný. Je dobrou praxou uchovávať zdroje pre environmentálne tvrdenia."

